data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME IS LOCATED IN THE SOUGHT AFTER BROOKSHIRE COMMUNITY AND WONT LAST LONG! CONVENIENTLY LOCATED RIGHT OFF I-575 EXIT 9. JUST MINUTES FROM THE OUTLET SHOPPES OF ATLANTA AND RESTAURANTS, COSTCO AND ALL THAT DOWNTOWN WOODSTOCK HAS TO OFFER. INCLUDING THE AMPHITHEATER, BREWERIES, SHOPPING, RESTAURANTS, BIKING TRAILS AND MORE. THE BROOKSHIRE COMMUNITY FEATURES 2 SWIMMING POOLS, 8 TENNIS COURTS, PICKLEBALL COURTS, PLAYGROUND AND A CLUBHOUSE. THE BEAUTIFUL HOME FEATURES 3 BR 2 BA UPSTAIRS WITH LAUNDRY ROOM. HVAC AND ROOF ONLY 5 YEARS OLD! HARDWOODS THROUGHOUT THE HOME. KITCHEN W/VIEW TO LIVING ROOM. SEPARATE DINING ROOM, BREAKFAST AREA, 2 STORY LIVING ROOM, MASTER BATH W/ GARDEN TUB AND SEPARATE SHOWER AND A CUSTOM WALK-IN CLOSET. THIS HOME WILL NOT DISAPPOINT.
